    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing to complain about the problem with my laptop which started a week ago. The issue is with power supply due to which the laptop shutdowns abruptly. Although I tried installing various software patches the issue still persists. It is a new laptop which was given to me a year ago when I started working from home.",
        "It is affecting my daily work due to which I am unable to complete my assignments on time. Moreover, I could not even join online meetings and replay emails quickly. If this problem persists I would not be able to work anymore.",
        "Would it be possible to fix this issue in a few days? Perhaps it would be a good idea to replace this laptop with a newer one so that this problem does not occur again. In case if this is not possible, please schedule maintenance service to repair this laptop. I would be glad if you could prioritize my request.",
        "I look forward to hearing from you.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Chris"
